Rating: 4
I usually don't make fish, but this turned out to be one great dish! Because my husband needs to watch his weight and cholesterol, I sauteed the scallions (no leeks around) in PAM. Also, I added a little water instead of the olive oil when making the bread crumb topping, and just gave the fillets a good spray of PAM before popping them into the oven. I used 2 tbsp of oil to 1 tbsp basalmic for the viagrette, and we found this dish was both healthy and delicious!!

